Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------ANIME-------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当想起我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那无名的教会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美好的家园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残败不堪却惹人怜爱的教会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有此时不在的那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  苦难正是不可或缺之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你拖着疲累的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经没什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有我这样的第三者在场的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以更好地看清事态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我整理一下当前的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  菲亚君怀疑是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形原黑绘君涉嫌镇上的连续杀人案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起疑的证据是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  受害者都是黑绘君店里的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目击了黑绘吸收受害者的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补充一点  我在新闻上看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害者除了被弄成箱型之外还缺损了一部分肢体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  遗体的一部分被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这样办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我监禁直到嫌疑洗脱为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想监禁自己的话  就随便你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的诅咒到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本还没有解除是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么丑恶的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么深恶的诅咒哪有可能这么轻易就被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让她静静吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙其实并不想怀疑黑绘的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此我不会再追究是不是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样  黑绘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监禁自己的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲亚她看到的那一幕的理由才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是诅咒带来的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是能力的一环  跟补充燃料差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我也隐约感觉到那是死者的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以带着吊唁的心情吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些好好跟菲亚说明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她听了之后会信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像被告知诅咒是不可能解除的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑克牌或者歌留多牌之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚很漫长的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此姐  监禁地方就选在稍远一些的房间就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑克牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者黄段子也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我刚才就想问了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春的「这个」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是第一次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但通过你的发言我大概了解你是怎样的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春亮君班上的班长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子不才  今后请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小女子不才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  被发现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起内讧可不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我想你们差不多该明白了所以来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经找到共通点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀害的人全是美容院的客人  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  你必须要认识到更深一层的共通点的意义才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四号机构
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搔式兽掌态  猫爪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15}{\pos(377,325)}Cat's  Paw
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法呢  是时候进行下一步的计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模式  缓冲的宗盛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  黑绘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要到哪里大闹一场才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得到处都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再见到你被活埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  为什么只把玻璃打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意在大家面前宣战却又临阵退缩  到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我多虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得我们现在是被分割开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  还真是一位头脑灵活的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我不觉得有任何困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印于镜子里的黑白世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15}Welcome  to  Other  Side
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑绘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:06:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  你还是不要乱动为好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想我们怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单明了地说就是  当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须担心黑绘小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是限制了她的行动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼和口则不受限制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是感谢你  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长你逃出去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  做出些奇怪举动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的脖子上就要流出像石榴汁似的果汁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  任你处置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  请你先进去这个货柜里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是非常美妙的甜蜜小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁质的粗糙感和冰冷太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它戴到手脚上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  想要些热乎乎的果汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你也来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入正题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是视频通告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  菲亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想他们三位平安归来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请您起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后将和我们一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧  菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  您不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上岂有无需经历苦难的救赎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇上连续不断的杀人案件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考其意义  究其真相  这就是苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们家族会来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以邀请你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想和你们在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想和你们一起喝茶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把我们也当作家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我们渴望成为你们的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为美好的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非人类的你们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人是值得爱怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人是值得救赎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人是理应认同的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了使家人真正成为家人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只有一个单纯的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比布利欧家族会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全盘肯定祸具这种存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说全盘肯定祸具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  肯定祸具的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  也包含其诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们肯定孕育出你们这些优越者的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用名为诅咒的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人任意摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认同你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接纳你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒是渴望杀人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请尽情屠杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒是使持有者发狂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请欣然地成为一名狂人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  诅咒是剥夺持有者性命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就欣然地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欣然地献上性命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我自己一点都不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对祸具的绝对献身和关怀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让这种家族爱觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才称得上是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  所以我才让家人们帮助了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  家人们都很高兴地为我而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说八道了  什么  这到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  这就是所谓的共通点？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  不是去了黑绘的店的客人被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是让将死之人光临了她的店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  还有一条提示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们全都带着十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难度是不是有点太高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救赎之前  必须让菲亚小姐你们经历苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而感受到我们家人的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一点都不明白你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有一点想提问的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害人的遗体缺失到底有什么含义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不过是食人调理法的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15}{\pos(342,325)}Cannibal  Cooker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯地想将人杀死然后吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  菲亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您明白现在的情况了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结论出来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请光临一同附上的地图所表示的地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此久候大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我坚决拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请大家稍作休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑绘  头发能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能动的话早动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门那边没有缝隙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀了我裙子之后还帮我整理裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理是整理了  但我可没有掀你的裙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这只是个意外的事故而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很平常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下觉得很平常才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是被监禁起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春他可老练了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神年龄已经是步履蹒跚的寺庙老主持的等级了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无计可施了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能等了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果只有我一个的话  恐怕已经陷入恐慌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有冷静的班长和黑绘在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才让我能这么放心的  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真正能拯救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是普通地打开门进来了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要戴上去存在感就会变稀薄的祸具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字由来于第一个戴上它的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士底狱的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15}Il  est  dans  Bastille
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才能进来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个面具的机能不仅是存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连佩戴者的行为都变得稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听别人讲话的态度可以得满分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜知君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没和他说吗  锥霞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是研究室长国的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上野锥霞的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是和你说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和家族会扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝·比布利欧·巴斯库利赫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿法衣的莞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(320,325)}Mother  of  Canonical
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称起始之A的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一母君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家族会开山的会长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为所有疯狂行为的发源的女人来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可赌大了呀  敢把你的那个展示出来  锥霞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会兴奋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你将来就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为你班长她才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍受到倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样被监禁起来又是因为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了夜知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的小鬼  烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  对夜知出手不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既没打他也没踢他呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把夜知的手铐解开…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锥霞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有救他们的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个面具只能多消除一个人的存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怪我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了又想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为答谢可以摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对小孩子没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己能不能活到明天还不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把夜知留在那个女人身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会被怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过和我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家族会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜知家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱型恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们相关的事件现象的话我还有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察他们是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都只为了研究吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  你就只是个道具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我们就像室长的道具一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是零件  齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从以前开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对暗曲拍明  对研究室长国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个蠢死了的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这些理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己喜欢的男人都救不了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道我到底为何而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事  无可救药地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  就我一个人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你脱离了那个叫研究室长国什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  已经愈合得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都能走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶牛女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我犯了错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀疑了黑绘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到应有的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你也认真地打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅诅诅…诅咒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做的惩罚也只有这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的应该让黑绘本人来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的事都无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是今后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用的东西全用上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管付出什么代价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要夺回应该夺回的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚君  此叶君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说夜知有能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得是什么样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春亮君的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来他只是个普通的人类而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是不被诅咒和无耻行为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有温柔和好人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有料理能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夜知春亮有伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我  像你们这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我赢了就把春亮还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你赢了就把我带走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期盼着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它受到更多的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为超越人类的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就像您这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会渴望诅咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四号机构
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搔式兽掌态
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫爪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十二章  超越者无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.89,0:23:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话诅咒你哦


